Source: qcnpuperf
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: samfreund-qc <freund@qti.qualcomm.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake, qcom-fastrpc-dev, qcom-dspservices-headers-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: libqcnpuperf1
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qualcomm NPU performance metrics library
 Runtime shared library providing NPU/DSP performance metrics
 on Qualcomm Linux platforms via FastRPC.

Package: libqcnpuperf-dev
Architecture: arm64
Depends: libqcnpuperf1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, qcom-fastrpc-dev
Description: Qualcomm NPU performance metrics library -- development files
 Headers and pkg-config file for building against libqcnpuperf.

Package: qcnpuperfd
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qualcomm NPU performance stats daemon
 Polls DSP_NPU0 once per second and writes NPU performance metrics
 to /tmp/qcnpuperf_stats using atomic rename. Designed to run
 under systemd on Qualcomm aarch64 Linux platforms.
